---
---

<section id="wine-and-dining" class="py-20 bg-cream">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="font-display italic text-gold text-lg mb-2">Eat, drink, and be merry</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-wine">Wine &amp; Dining</h2>
      <p class="ornament text-gold/50 text-sm mt-4">&mdash; &#10049; &mdash;</p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-charcoal/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We&rsquo;re in the heart of Burgundy &mdash; one of the world&rsquo;s great wine regions.
        Here are our top picks for wineries to visit and restaurants to enjoy.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Wineries -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-wine mb-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span>🍇</span> Wineries &amp; Tastings
      </h3>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">

        <a href="https://www.chateaudecouches.com/fr_FR/oenotourisme" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
           class="block bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal group-hover:text-wine transition-colors">Ch&acirc;teau de Couches</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60 mt-2">
            Castle visit + guided tasting of 6 wines from the C&ocirc;tes du Couchois.
            The &ldquo;Clos Marguerite&rdquo; is their star wine, with roots back to 1586.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-charcoal/50">
            <span>📍 25 min</span>
            <span>&euro;14 combined ticket</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.autun-tourisme.com/offres/chanson-beaune-fr-3478154/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
           class="block bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal group-hover:text-wine transition-colors">Domaine Chanson, Beaune</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60 mt-2">
            One of Beaune&rsquo;s oldest wine houses (est. 1750). 88 hectares, mostly Premier Cru.
            Tours of their unique above-ground cellars with passionate guides.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-charcoal/50">
            <span>📍 40 min</span>
            <span>Reservations recommended</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.autun-tourisme.com/decouvrez/instant-gourmand-specialites-bourguignonnes/la-route-des-vins-et-le-couchois/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
           class="block bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal group-hover:text-wine transition-colors">Route des Vins du Couchois</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60 mt-2">
            A self-drive wine route through local villages. Fruity reds and charming whites
            from small producers, with rolling hills and bocage landscapes.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-charcoal/50">
            <span>📍 Starts 20 min away</span>
            <span>Self-guided</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.delicave.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
           class="block bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal group-hover:text-wine transition-colors">Caveau D&eacute;licave, Beaune</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60 mt-2">
            Wine tasting in a gorgeous 16th-century cellar in the heart of Beaune.
            Established since 1978, with an incredible selection of Burgundy wines.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-charcoal/50">
            <span>📍 40 min</span>
            <span>Open daily</span>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Restaurants -->
    <div>
      <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-wine mb-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span>🍽️</span> Restaurants
      </h3>
      <p class="text-center text-charcoal/60 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto text-sm">
        Several group meals are planned at the venue, but for evenings off you might want to
        explore these local restaurants. Book ahead for larger groups.
      </p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

        <a href="http://lechateaubriant.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
           class="block bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal group-hover:text-wine transition-colors">Le Ch&acirc;teaubriant</h4>
            <span class="text-xs bg-wine-50 text-wine px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Top Pick</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">
            Classic Burgundy gastronomy in a charming family-run restaurant.
            B&oelig;uf bourguignon, charolaise beef, escargots. Excellent wine list.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-xs text-charcoal/50">
            <p>📍 Autun &middot; 20 min drive</p>
            <p>💰 Menus &euro;20-65 &middot; Kids menu &euro;10</p>
            <p>📞 03 85 52 21 58</p>
            <p>🕐 Tue-Sat lunch &amp; dinner</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="https://labrasseriedeshalles.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
           class="block bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal group-hover:text-wine transition-colors">La Brasserie des Halles</h4>
            <span class="text-xs bg-gold/20 text-gold-dark px-2 py-1 rounded-full">4.5/5</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">
            Burgundy cuisine and wine bar with seasonal, locally-sourced dishes.
            Fondue bourguignonne, fresh fish, and a lovely ambiance.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-xs text-charcoal/50">
            <p>📍 Nolay &middot; 30 min drive</p>
            <p>📞 03 80 20 64 40</p>
            <p>🕐 Reservations recommended</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="https://fr.restaurantguru.com/Au-Tire-Bouchon-Nolay" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
           class="block bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal group-hover:text-wine transition-colors">Au Tire Bouchon</h4>
            <span class="text-xs bg-gold/20 text-gold-dark px-2 py-1 rounded-full">4.5/5</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">
            Traditional French cuisine with a lovely outdoor terrace. Known for their
            b&oelig;uf bourguignon and local cheeses.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-xs text-charcoal/50">
            <p>📍 Nolay &middot; 30 min drive</p>
            <p>💰 &euro;20-30 per person</p>
            <p>🕐 Tue-Sun lunch &amp; dinner</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.autun-tourisme.com/offres/a-lheure-des-saveurs-couches-fr-4999013/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
           class="block bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal group-hover:text-wine transition-colors mb-3">A l&rsquo;Heure des Saveurs</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">
            Regional Burgundy cuisine with a terrace. 78 covers.
            Fresh weekend menus &amp; takeaway options.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-xs text-charcoal/50">
            <p>📍 Couches &middot; 25 min drive</p>
            <p>🕐 Mon-Tue, Thu-Sun lunch; Sat dinner</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="https://pizza-leo-71.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
           class="block bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal group-hover:text-wine transition-colors mb-3">Pizza L&eacute;o</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">
            Artisan pizzas &amp; burgers right in Epinac. 40+ pizza varieties, fresh local
            ingredients. Takeaway, delivery, and food truck available for events.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-xs text-charcoal/50">
            <p>📍 Epinac &middot; In town!</p>
            <p>💰 &euro;9-14.50</p>
            <p>📞 07 61 02 52 54</p>
            <p>🕐 Tue-Sun</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="https://hotel-legrandcafe.fr/restaurant-Epinac" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
           class="block bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-charcoal group-hover:text-wine transition-colors mb-3">Le Grand Caf&eacute;</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">
            Hotel-restaurant in Autun with a brasserie serving daily menus, plats du jour,
            and local wines. Casual and family-friendly.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-xs text-charcoal/50">
            <p>📍 Autun &middot; 20 min drive</p>
            <p>📞 03 85 52 27 66</p>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
